# SOCIALCLUB::SC_COMMUNITY_EVENT_GET_EXTRA_DATA_INT

## Summary
Get the values of extra data for the ACTIVE social club event (if there is one active)

## Parameters
* **STRING** name
* **INT\*** value

## Returns
* **BOOL**:
True if the value was found an returned.
OTherwise false.
